column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z, p.petroR5#_r, p.fracdeV_r, p.deVRad_r, p.expRad_r, n.distance, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, s.velDisp FROM fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) n JOIN PhotoObj AS p on p.objid = n.objid JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = n.objid WHERE s.class = GALAXY AGN BROADLINE
